CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: The Fund invests principally in the equity and equity-linked securities of what it believes to be rapidly growing venture-capital-backed emerging companies, primarily in the United States. The Fund may also invest on an opportunistic basis in select U.S. publicly traded equity securities or certain non-U.S. companies that otherwise meet the investment criteria. The Funds investment objective is to maximize the portfolios total return.
